<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 16:08:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>土耳其领导人称以色列总理“与希特勒没有什么不同”后，埃尔多安和内塔尼亚胡互斥</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/erdogan-netanyahu-trade-barbs-after-turkey-leader-compares-israeli-pm-to-hitler/0000018c-abcf-d45c-a98e-abcf6fcd0000</link><description>“内塔尼亚胡所做的事情比希特勒所做的事情还少吗？”事实并非如此，”埃尔多安说。内塔尼亚胡回应称，埃尔多安应该是最后一个对以色列说教的人，称他正在对库尔德人实施种族灭绝，并保持着监禁记者的世界纪录</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:50:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/erdogan-netanyahu-trade-barbs-after-turkey-leader-compares-israeli-pm-to-hitler/0000018c-abcf-d45c-a98e-abcf6fcd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队无人机袭击约旦河西岸难民营，造成六名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/six-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-army-drone-attack-on-west-bank-refugee-camp/0000018c-ab8e-d22d-a3dd-bfff58b40000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，这六人是一群恐怖分子，他们一直向在该地区活动的部队投掷爆炸装置。近几个月来，以色列军队加强了在约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦城市图尔卡尔姆附近努尔沙姆斯难民营的行动</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/six-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-army-drone-attack-on-west-bank-refugee-camp/0000018c-ab8e-d22d-a3dd-bfff58b40000</guid></item><item><title>12 个议程设置《国土报》播客剧集讲述 2023 年的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-timeline/.premium/12-agenda-setting-haaretz-podcast-episodes-that-tell-the-story-of-2023/0000018c-a56a-d97c-a9ec-bfefa18b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:26:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-timeline/.premium/12-agenda-setting-haaretz-podcast-episodes-that-tell-the-story-of-2023/0000018c-a56a-d97c-a9ec-bfefa18b0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗革命卫队：10月7日以色列发生的袭击是对卡西姆·苏莱马尼遇刺事件的回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/irans-revolutionary-guard-oct-7-attack-was-in-response-to-soleimani-assassination/0000018c-abb7-d044-a5fd-ebbf050b0000</link><description>哈马斯很快否认了伊朗革命卫队的说法，这表明它参与策划了 10 月 7 日对以色列南部的袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:20:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/irans-revolutionary-guard-oct-7-attack-was-in-response-to-soleimani-assassination/0000018c-abb7-d044-a5fd-ebbf050b0000</guid></item><item><title>第一位以色列依良心拒服加沙战争者被判入狱：“我知道这是正确的事情”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/first-israeli-conscientious-objector-of-gaza-war-is-jailed-im-doing-the-right-thing/0000018c-ab74-d885-abdf-ff7e09890000</link><description>18 岁的塔尔·米特尼克周二拒绝应征入伍，目前正在军事监狱服刑 30 天。他在宣判前夕表示，政府希望“加深占领并不允许任何形式的异议”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/first-israeli-conscientious-objector-of-gaza-war-is-jailed-im-doing-the-right-thing/0000018c-ab74-d885-abdf-ff7e09890000</guid></item><item><title>在哈马斯袭击之前不久，这个警告就出现了。帕加前哨发生了什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/shortly-before-the-hamas-attack-this-warning-arrived-what-happened-at-the-paga-outpost/0000018c-a631-dc33-a78c-bfb9f5360000</link><description>R. 正在前往检查是否有渗透嫌疑的途中，却被禁止靠近围栏。两小时后，哈马斯开始发起进攻 ■ 少数士兵阻止了数十名试图占领纳哈尔奥兹基布兹附近军事哨所的恐怖分子。十二名士兵被杀，他们的父母想要答案</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/shortly-before-the-hamas-attack-this-warning-arrived-what-happened-at-the-paga-outpost/0000018c-a631-dc33-a78c-bfb9f5360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列面临的真正危险先于哈马斯袭击 — — 并且仍然是最大的威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/real-danger-facing-israel-precedes-hamas-attack-and-remains-biggest-threat/0000018c-ab1b-d885-abdf-ff5f75ce0000</link><description>去年出去抗议的数十万以色列人乐观地认为，内塔尼亚胡的司法政变已经随着他的支持率下降而消退。但制度和社会的衰败在最近几个月才加速，一些人已经付出了代价</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 14:58:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/real-danger-facing-israel-precedes-hamas-attack-and-remains-biggest-threat/0000018c-ab1b-d885-abdf-ff5f75ce0000</guid></item><item><title>妇女节——以及您从未听说过的其他犹太庆祝活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-festival-of-women-and-other-jewish-celebrations-you-never-heard-of/0000018c-ab3d-d885-abdf-ff7f7fd70000</link><description>达莉亚·马克思拉比在她的新书《从时间到时间》中探讨了犹太历中一些鲜为人知的日期，其中包括经常被边缘化的声音</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 13:36:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-festival-of-women-and-other-jewish-celebrations-you-never-heard-of/0000018c-ab3d-d885-abdf-ff7f7fd70000</guid></item><item><title>两次加沙战争：为何以色列人和外来者之间的鸿沟如此巨大且令人震惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/two-gaza-wars-why-the-gulf-between-israelis-and-outsiders-is-so-vast-and-jarring/0000018c-aade-d885-abdf-fede81470000</link><description>“我们尝试过和平”和“现在不是时候”等观念，以及从 10 月 7 日开始的一系列压缩的历史，正在推动以色列人和巴勒斯坦人远离加沙战争的政治解决方案</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 13:34:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/two-gaza-wars-why-the-gulf-between-israelis-and-outsiders-is-so-vast-and-jarring/0000018c-aade-d885-abdf-fede81470000</guid></item><item><title>真主党将决定以色列政府及其领导人的命运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-will-decide-fate-of-israels-government-and-its-leader/0000018c-aaae-d462-afbe-aeef53800000</link><description>随着黎巴嫩边境局势升温，全面战争的可能性越来越大，有关推翻内塔尼亚胡的讨论已经降温，甘茨退出紧急政府的日子越来越遥远</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 12:46:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-will-decide-fate-of-israels-government-and-its-leader/0000018c-aaae-d462-afbe-aeef53800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼议员呼吁在加沙北部建立定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/israel-should-establish-jewish-settlements-in-northern-gaza-far-right-lawmaker-says/0000018c-aaab-d462-afbe-aeef6bac0000</link><description>“占领加沙河以北的一切，直到内蒂夫哈萨拉的犹太社区。明天早上，整个北部地区将成为一个新的犹太社区。立法者 Tzivka Foghel 表示，欢迎任何想将 Al-Shifa 医院保留为博物馆的人</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 10:58:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/israel-should-establish-jewish-settlements-in-northern-gaza-far-right-lawmaker-says/0000018c-aaab-d462-afbe-aeef6bac0000</guid></item><item><title>受伤的以色列士兵死于真菌感染；医学专家称并非加沙独有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/wounded-israeli-soldier-dies-of-fungal-infection-medical-experts-not-exclusive-to-gaza/0000018c-aa4c-df5f-a79c-ea6f9ba60000</link><description>传染病专家告诉《国土报》，以色列士兵接触可能引起感染的细菌和真菌的情况很少，而且不一定是加沙地带独有的，这些感染主要发生在重伤患者身上</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 09:40:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/wounded-israeli-soldier-dies-of-fungal-infection-medical-experts-not-exclusive-to-gaza/0000018c-aa4c-df5f-a79c-ea6f9ba60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军军官和两名士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/idf-officer-two-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-a9d9-dbb4-af9f-edf9d3d90000</link><description>以色列军队周三宣布三名士兵死亡，使自10月7日以来阵亡士兵总数达到498人</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 06:11:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/idf-officer-two-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-a9d9-dbb4-af9f-edf9d3d90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列希望重点打击哈马斯，但杀害伊朗指挥官可能导致北部局势升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-to-focus-on-hamas-but-killing-of-iranian-commander-risks-northern-escalation/0000018c-a7f1-d7f7-a7ce-fffd62040000</link><description>自10月7日恐怖袭击以来，伊朗一直没有积极参与战争，但公开支持哈马斯。现在看来，以色列的克制已经结束了 ■ 计划对哈马斯造成更多破坏的以色列国防军正在发出这样的信息：该组织无法在这场冲突中幸存下来 ■ 以色列人质的家人继续战斗，但绝望正在加剧</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 04:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-to-focus-on-hamas-but-killing-of-iranian-commander-risks-northern-escalation/0000018c-a7f1-d7f7-a7ce-fffd62040000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列国防军深入加沙汗尤尼斯，对以色列北部的袭击加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-live/u-s-israel-discuss-policy-for-day-after-conflict-idf-chief-war-will-last-many-months/0000018c-a957-d7f7-a7ce-f97fd1670000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的三名士兵的名字 ■ 巴勒斯坦人：约旦河西岸无人机袭击造成六人死亡 ■ 美国对国际原子能机构关于伊朗铀浓缩活动增加的报告“深表关切” ■ 以色列军队解散了定居者部队的五名士兵 ■ 以色列军队深化在汗的地面行动尤尼斯 ■ 自10月7日以来，以色列至少有1,300名平民和士兵被杀；至少 130 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 21,110 人死亡，55,243 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 03:45:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-live/u-s-israel-discuss-policy-for-day-after-conflict-idf-chief-war-will-last-many-months/0000018c-a957-d7f7-a7ce-f97fd1670000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼本格维尔违反与内塔尼亚胡的协议，告诉以色列监狱长他不会延长她的合同</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ben-gvir-tells-israels-prison-chief-he-wont-extend-her-contract/0000018c-a80b-dbb4-af9f-ed6ba0df0000</link><description>国家安全部长以缺乏信任和多次失败为由，决定不延长凯蒂·佩里的合同——尽管他无权这样做</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 21:54:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ben-gvir-tells-israels-prison-chief-he-wont-extend-her-contract/0000018c-a80b-dbb4-af9f-ed6ba0df0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列还是哈马斯？现在说谁会赢得这场战争还为时过早</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-or-hamas-its-too-early-to-say-whos-winning-the-war/0000018c-a77d-dd77-a59e-fffd6e940000</link><description>以色列尚未摧毁哈马斯的领导和指挥结构也就不足为奇了。双方都为这场战争做好了准备，并充分利用了各自截然不同的优势</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 20:13:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-or-hamas-its-too-early-to-say-whos-winning-the-war/0000018c-a77d-dd77-a59e-fffd6e940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向英特尔提供32亿美元赠款，以推进芯片工厂史无前例的扩张</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/israel-grants-intel-3-2-billion-grant-to-advance-unprecedented-expansion-of-chip-plant/0000018c-a6dc-dd77-a59e-ffdd01230000</link><description>以色列有史以来最大的私人投资被认为是一家美国公司对以色列在加沙地面行动的支持的主要表现</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 17:31:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/israel-grants-intel-3-2-billion-grant-to-advance-unprecedented-expansion-of-chip-plant/0000018c-a6dc-dd77-a59e-ffdd01230000</guid></item><item><title>两极分化：以色列和加沙战争迫使年轻的美国犹太人选边站</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/polarized-israel-gaza-war-is-forcing-young-u-s-jews-to-choose-sides/0000018c-a608-db79-abee-f6ad3b1d0000</link><description>一些人正在加强亲以色列的活动，而另一些人则渴望“一个非犹太复国主义或反犹太复国主义的犹太公共空间”。赌注太高，不能袖手旁观</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 17:26:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/polarized-israel-gaza-war-is-forcing-young-u-s-jews-to-choose-sides/0000018c-a608-db79-abee-f6ad3b1d0000</guid></item><item><title>从黎巴嫩向教堂发射的反坦克导弹造成九名以色列士兵和一名平民受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/anti-tank-missile-fired-from-lebanon-at-church-wounds-israeli-nine-soldiers-one-civilian/0000018c-a6ae-dd77-a59e-ffaf6d720000</link><description>一枚反坦克导弹袭击以色列北部巴勒斯坦基督教村庄的一座教堂大院，击中一名 80 岁的平民。以色列士兵赶到现场疏散他，却被另一枚导弹击中</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 16:19:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/anti-tank-missile-fired-from-lebanon-at-church-wounds-israeli-nine-soldiers-one-civilian/0000018c-a6ae-dd77-a59e-ffaf6d720000</guid></item></channel></rss>